  [ Niels Thykier ]
  * dh_bugfiles: Fix regression in installing the reportbug
    script correctly.  Thanks to Jakub Wilk for reporting.
    (Closes: #784648)

  [ Translation updates ]
  * pt - Thanks to Américo Monteiro.
    (Closes: #784582)

