debhelper (8.9.8) unstable; urgency=low

  * dh_fixperms: Operate on .ali files throughout /usr/lib, including
    multiarch dirs. Closes: #641279
  * dh: Avoid compat deprecation warning before option parsing.
    Closes: #641361
