  * dh_strip: Man page reference to policy section on DEB_BUILD_OPTIONS.
    Closes: #437337
  * dh_link: Skip self-links. Closes: #438572
  * Don't use - in front of make clean in example rules files.
  * Typo. Closes: #441272

